OL,3,CMan in hospital after being shot in
OL,4,Chand in Coleraine
OL,6,FA man has been taken to hospital after
OL,7,Fbeing shot in Coleraine.
OL,9,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,10,Fafter four shots were fired at the man
OL,11,Fwhile he was walking home between 1am
OL,12,Fand 1.30am on Sunday on Bushmills Road.
OL,14,FOne of the shots hit the victim in the
OL,15,Fhand, and police said he was being
OL,16,Ftreated in hospital.
OL,18,FThe PSNI said the gunman was
OL,19,Freportedly "dressed all in black with
OL,20,Fhis face covered".
OL,26,@{D@LOU|D@QO]
