OL,3,CMan in hospital after being shot in
OL,4,Chand in Coleraine
OL,6,FBushmills Road was closed from the
OL,7,Fjunction of the Ballycastle Road to
OL,8,Fthe junction with Artillery Road as
OL,9,Fpolice conducted inquiries.
OL,11,FA PSNI spokeswoman asked for anyone in
OL,12,Fthe area at the time and who may have
OL,13,Frelevant dashcam, doorbell or other
OL,14,Fvideo footage to ring 101, quoting
OL,15,Freference number 443 12/04/26.
